irtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-sunset-prayer-salat-al-maghrib","tag-voluntary-prayers-salat-nafilah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9ty","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/02\/12-rakaat-al-sunan-al-rawatib\/","url_meta":{"origin":36428,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Twelve raka\u2019at of al-Sunan al-Rawatib prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever perseveres in performing twelve cycles of prayer from the Sunnah, Allah will build a house for him in Paradise. They are four cycles before noon prayer and two after it, two cycles after sunset prayer, two\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36424,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/sunan-maghrib-isha\/","url_meta":{"origin":36428,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary prayer between Maghrib and Isha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: In regards to the verse, \u201cThey arise from their beds, calling upon their Lord in fear and in hope, spending from what We have provided them,\u201d (32:16). Anas said, \u201cThey are those who are awake to pray between sunset and evening prayer.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36437,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/31\/added-salat-al-witr\/","url_meta":{"origin":36428,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Witr: Allah added Witr prayer, so perform it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 31, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Basrah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty has added one to your prayers, so perform it between the evening and dawn prayers: the Witr prayer, the Witr prayer.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 27229 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0635\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u063a\u0641\u0627\u0631\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34452,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/05\/five-salawat-protect-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":36428,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Five prayers protect believers from the Fire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou are exposed to fire, you are exposed to fire! If you perform the dawn prayer, it will cleanse you. Then, you are exposed to fire, you are exposed to fire! If you perform the noon prayer,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25400,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/09\/combine-salat-traveling\/","url_meta":{"origin":36428,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Travel: The Prophet combined prayers during travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 9, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, combined sunset and evening\u00a0prayers if he was undertaking a journey. And Ibn Abbas said, \u201cThe Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, combined the noon prayers and afternoon prayers\u00a0if he was on a journey, as well as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28121,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/ten-rakaat-sunan\/","url_meta":{"origin":36428,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Voluntary Sunan prayers throughout day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I prayed with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, two prostrations before and after noon prayer, two prostrations after sunset prayer, two prostrations after evening prayer, and two prostrations after Friday prayer. As for sunset and evening prayer, they were in his house. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-jso